name: The Android and The Chicken
description: 1-to-1 with the physical artwork and I will send the actual work to the collector. This is a drawing on acid free paper (size:A4) with ballpoint pen and colour pencils. The actual physical work together will be sent to the collector with registered post (regardless of the collectors location). After the purchase I will need owners  postal address and Tezos wallet. If the beginning and end of the wallet is matching the owners wallet, I will send 1 tez for confirmation. When the transaction goes thru I will post the artwork. Postage is included in the price. Collectors can check the authenticity of the work in my Instagram account (@nulnul7).  You can reach me from the email in my profile, Twitter (@nulnul7_art) or Instagram..
